io.flutter.plugin.common

Interface MessageCodec<T>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BinaryCodec, JSONMessageCodec, StandardMessageCodec, StringCodec

    public interface MessageCodec<T>
    A message encoding/decoding mechanism. Both operations throw IllegalArgumentException, if conversion fails.

    • Method Summary

        Decodes the specified message from binary.
        Parameters:
        message - the ByteBuffer message, possibly null.
        Returns:
